section.title: Which packages are marked as maintainer-needed

body.p: Packages which do not have an active maintainer to take care of them are marked as maintainer-needed. This means that they will gonna rot or be removed from portage tree unless someone steps up and take care of them. You are free to do it your self if you feel like it. More information about maintainer-needed packages you may find on treecleaners project page.
The following 722 packages are marked as maintainer-needed ( daily generated list )
